column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/p4504_43f510d37d680ca4347878d2fb6f8b97b54e7611/ for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-te
I'm not happy with this, as I said it's IMHO no real alternative, but seems to me like pure refactoring.\n
